Request Your Personalized Demo





  &lt;label for="fullName" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;Full Name*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="fullName" name="fullName" required style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide your full name.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="email" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;Business Email*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" required style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide a valid email address.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="company" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;Company Name*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="company" name="company" required style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide your company name.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="phone" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;Phone Number&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phone" name="phone" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="jobTitle" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;Job Title*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;input type="text" class="form-control" id="jobTitle" name="jobTitle" required style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please provide your job title.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="companySize" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;Company Size*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;select class="form-select" id="companySize" name="companySize" required style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
    &lt;option value="" selected disabled&gt;Select company size&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="1-50"&gt;1-50 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="51-200"&gt;51-200 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="201-500"&gt;201-500 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="501-1000"&gt;501-1000 employees&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="1001+"&gt;1001+ employees&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;/select&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please select your company size.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
  &lt;label for="iso27001Status" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;ISO 27001 Status*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;select class="form-select" id="iso27001Status" name="iso27001Status" required style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;
    &lt;option value="" selected disabled&gt;Select your status&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Not started"&gt;Not started yet&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Planning"&gt;Planning phase&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Implementation"&gt;Implementation in progress&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Pre-certification"&gt;Preparing for certification&lt;/option&gt;
    &lt;option value="Certified"&gt;Already certified&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;/select&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;Please select your ISO 27001 status.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-4"&gt;
  &lt;label for="message" class="form-label" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;Additional Information&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;textarea class="form-control" id="message" name="message" rows="4" style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); color: var(--kudoo-light-text); padding: 0.8rem; border-radius: 4px;"&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class="mb-3 form-check"&gt;
  &lt;input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="privacy" required style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);"&gt;
  &lt;label class="form-check-label" for="privacy" style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;I agree to Kudoo's &lt;a href="privacy.qmd" style="color: var(--kudoo-green);"&gt;Privacy Policy&lt;/a&gt;*&lt;/label&gt;
  &lt;div class="invalid-feedback"&gt;You must agree to our Privacy Policy.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;button type="submit" class="cta-btn" style="width: 100%;"&gt;Request Demo&lt;/button&gt;


:::



What to Expect Next



Confirmation Email: You’ll receive an immediate confirmation of your demo request.


Scheduling Call: A Kudoo representative will contact you within one business day to schedule your demo at a convenient time.


Pre-Demo Questionnaire: We’ll send a brief questionnaire to understand your specific needs and customize the demonstration accordingly.


Personalized Demonstration: Attend a live, interactive demonstration of the Kudoo GRC platform tailored to your requirements.


Follow-Up Resources: After the demo, you’ll receive additional materials and access to a trial environment to explore the platform further.



&lt;h4 style="color: var(--kudoo-blue);"&gt;Demo Preparation Tip&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p style="color: var(--kudoo-light-text);"&gt;To get the most from your demo, consider inviting key stakeholders from your information security, IT, and compliance teams to participate. This ensures all perspectives are represented during the demonstration.&lt;/p&gt;



